    "type": "Boundaries",
    "difficulty": "hard",
    "passage": "The grant will support three interdisciplinary research teams: a group of marine biologists tracking coral bleaching, primarily in the western Pacific ______ a team of civil engineers modeling urban flood risk; and a coalition of historians and chemists analyzing the pigments of ancient manuscripts.",
