    "prompt": "A factory produces widgets on two assembly lines. Line 1 produces 60% of the widgets, and Line 2 produces the remaining 40%. Of the widgets made on Line 1, 5% are defective, and of the widgets made on Line 2, 8% are defective. If a randomly selected widget is found to be defective, what is the probability that it was made on Line 2?",
